@startuml
state "Waiting for Withdrawal Amount" as WaitingAmount
state "Selecting Predefined Amount" as SelectingPredefined
state "Entering Custom Amount" as EnteringCustom
state "Transaction Cancelled" as TransactionCancelled
state "Card Returned" as CardReturned

[*] --> WaitingAmount [*]
WaitingAmount --> SelectingPredefined : select predefined amount
SelectingPredefined --> WaitingAmount : cancel selection
WaitingAmount --> EnteringCustom : enter custom amount
EnteringCustom --> WaitingAmount : cancel entry
WaitingAmount --> TransactionCancelled : cancel transaction
TransactionCancelled --> CardReturned : return card

note right of WaitingAmount: User selects or enters withdrawal amount.
note left of SelectingPredefined: Predefined amounts are provided for selection.

@enduml
